data.title: Dell's Guide to SXSWi
data.meta_description: Dell's Guide to SXSWi - Download as a PDF or view online for free
data.text:
1. Dell’s Guide to SXSWi March 2012

2. The Dell SXSWi experience • Dell hosted its first ever external facing “Unconference,” March 8th, 2012, the day before SXSWi kicked off, with a variety of SMB professionals and social media thought leaders • We had over 45 attendees representing multiple countries • The day was broken into 4 groups of sessions led by attendees who discussed their specific area of interest • A visual note-taker was on hand to record the Unconference and was also utilized to capture a variety of relevant sessions for the SMB audience at SXSWi • Throughout the weekend, via the Dell SB & Entrepreneur SXSWi concierge team, a branded presence was established in multiple locations to hand out refreshments, and discuss how the overall SXSWi experience with attendees #DellSXSW
